stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unmonitored
    Unmonitored --> Deploying : Trigger Deployment
    Deploying --> Configuring : Ansible runs
    Configuring --> Running : Agents started
    Running --> SendingMetrics : Node Exporter/cAdvisor
    Running --> SendingLogs : Filebeat
    SendingMetrics --> Alerting : Threshold exceeded
    Alerting --> IncidentCreated : Auto-incident
    IncidentCreated --> Resolved : Operator fixes
    Resolved --> Running
